Name: Giuliano de' Medici, Duke of Nemours
Relationship with predecessor: Brother of Cardinal Giovanni de' Medici, third son of Lorenzo the Magnificent.

Name: Lorenzo II de' Medici, Duke of Urbino
Relationship with predecessor: Nephew of Giuliano de' Medici, Duke of Nemours, son of Piero the Unfortunate.

Name: Cardinal Giulio de' Medici
Relationship with predecessor: Cousin of Lorenzo II de' Medici, Duke of Urbino, son of Giuliano de' Medici who was the brother of Lorenzo the Magnificent. Elected to the Papacy, becoming Pope Clement VII.

Name: Cardinal Ippolito de' Medici
Relationship with predecessor: Cousin of Cardinal Giulio de' Medici, illegitimate son of Giuliano de' Medici, Duke of Nemours.
